と蛙の神聖なる相撲","chapter":6,"page_id":null,"scene_id":"choju_giga_1_06","sort_key":600,"title_en":"The Sacred Sumo Contest Between Rabbit and Frog","scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_first"},{"cat":"scene_title","title":"猿、双六盤を運ぶ","chapter":7,"page_id":null,"scene_id":"choju_giga_1_07","sort_key":700,"title_en":"Monkey Bearing the Sugoroku Game Board","scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_first"},{"cat":"scene_title","title":"猿僧正、年忌法要を司る","chapter":8,"page_id":null,"scene_id":"choju_giga_1_08","sort_key":800,"title_en":"The Monkey High Priest Conducting the Annual Memorial Rites","scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_first"},{"cat":"scene_title","title":"猿僧正へ奉げられた供物","chapter":9,"page_id":null,"scene_id":"choju_giga_1_09","sort_key":900,"title_en":"Sacred Offerings Presented to the Monkey High Priest","scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_first"}],"metadata":{"id":1,"era":"平安","title":"鳥獣人物戯画絵巻 甲巻","author":"鳥羽僧正覚猷","source":{"url":"https://colbase.nich.go.jp/collection_items/tnm/A-1530?locale=ja","name":"鳥獣人戯画絵巻 摸本（ColBase）"},"keyword":[{"id":"annualevent","name":"年中行事","slug":"annualevent"},{"id":"animal","name":"動物","slug":"animal"},{"id":"caricature","name":"戯画","slug":"caricature"},{"id":"buddhism","name":"仏教","slug":"buddhism"},{"id":"tobae","name":"鳥羽絵","slug":"tobae"}],"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_first","personname":[],"description":"平安時代（12世紀）に描かれた「鳥獣人物戯画絵巻」の甲巻の摸本です。猿と蛙の喧嘩や兎と蛙の相撲をはじめ、田楽や賭弓など、当時の京都で流行していたさまざまな遊びに動物たちが興じる様子が、豊かな表情で描かれています。元々はもっと長大な絵巻だったと考えられています。誰もが知る有名なシーンが、絵巻のどの場面に描かれているかを想像しながら、絵巻を広げて楽しんでみましょう。"}},{"emakis":[{"cat":null,"title":null,"chapter":null,"page_id":null,"scene_id":null,"sort_key":null,"title_en":null,"scroll_id":null},{"cat":"image","src":"v1771810795/emakimono/choju-jinbutsu-giga_first_12-375.jpg","name":"image","width":660,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":1,"page_id":null,"sort_key":101,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_second"},{"cat":"image","src":"v1771810786/emakimono/choju-jinbutsu-giga_first_11-375.jpg","name":"image","width":370,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":2,"page_id":null,"sort_key":202,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_second"},{"cat":"image","src":"v1771810478/emakimono/choju-jinbutsu-giga_first_07-375.jpg","name":"image","width":641,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":3,"page_id":null,"sort_key":303,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_second"},{"cat":"image","src":"v1771665962/emakimono/choju-jinbutsu-giga_first_04-375.jpg","name":"image","width":791,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":4,"page_id":null,"sort_key":404,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_second"}],"metadata":{"id":2,"era":"平安","title":"鳥獣人物戯画絵巻 乙巻","author":"鳥羽僧正覚猷","source":{"url":"https://colbase.nich.go.jp/collection_items/tnm/A-1530?locale=ja","name":"鳥獣人戯画絵巻 摸本（ColBase）"},"keyword":[{"id":"annualevent","name":"年中行事","slug":"annualevent"},{"id":"animal","name":"動物","slug":"animal"},{"id":"caricature","name":"戯画","slug":"caricature"},{"id":"buddhism","name":"仏教","slug":"buddhism"},{"id":"tobae","name":"鳥羽絵","slug":"tobae"},{"id":"spiritualbeast","name":"霊獣","slug":"spiritualbeast"}],"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_second","personname":[],"description":"平安時代（12世紀）に描かれた「鳥獣人物戯画絵巻」乙巻の摸本です。「動物尽くし」の図鑑のような一巻で、絵師の手習いの一環として作られたとも言われています。前半では「日本に生息する動物」をテーマに、馬や牛など、当時身近な動物たちが描かれています。後半では一転して、「日本に生息しない動物や霊獣」が描かれ、玄武や麒麟といった空想上の動物や、象や虎など日本には存在しない動物が、豊かな想像力を交えて表現されています。"}},{"emakis":[{"cat":null,"title":null,"chapter":null,"page_id":null,"scene_id":null,"sort_key":null,"title_en":null,"scroll_id":null},{"cat":"image","src":"v1771810795/emakimono/choju-jinbutsu-giga_first_12-375.jpg","name":"image","width":660,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":1,"page_id":null,"sort_key":101,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_third"},{"cat":"image","src":"v1771810786/emakimono/choju-jinbutsu-giga_first_11-375.jpg","name":"image","width":370,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":2,"page_id":null,"sort_key":202,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_third"},{"cat":"image","src":"v1771810478/emakimono/choju-jinbutsu-giga_first_07-375.jpg","name":"image","width":641,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":3,"page_id":null,"sort_key":303,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_third"},{"cat":"image","src":"v1771665962/emakimono/choju-jinbutsu-giga_first_04-375.jpg","name":"image","width":791,"config":"cloudinary","height":375,"chapter":4,"page_id":null,"sort_key":404,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_third"}],"metadata":{"id":3,"era":"平安","title":"鳥獣人物戯画絵巻 丙巻","author":"鳥羽僧正覚猷","source":{"url":"https://colbase.nich.go.jp/collection_items/tnm/A-1530?locale=ja","name":"鳥獣人戯画絵巻 摸本（ColBase）"},"keyword":[{"id":"caricature","name":"戯画","slug":"caricature"},{"id":"animal","name":"動物","slug":"animal"},{"id":"tobae","name":"鳥羽絵","slug":"tobae"},{"id":"annualevent","name":"年中行事","slug":"annualevent"},{"id":"buddhism","name":"仏教","slug":"buddhism"},{"id":"tobae","name":"鳥羽絵","slug":"tobae"}],"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_third","personname":[],"description":"平安～鎌倉時代（12世紀～13世紀）にかけて描かれた「鳥獣人物戯画絵巻」丙巻の摸本です。この巻では、初めて人間が登場します。前半では、双六や目比べなどを庶民が楽しんでいる様子が、「人間の戯画」として生き生きと描かれています。後半では、一転して、甲巻に戻ったかのように蛙や猿が競馬や蹴鞠に興じる様子が描かれます。前半と後半は、元々料紙の裏表に描かれていた可能性があり、そのため、描かれた時代や絵師が異なるのではないかという指摘もあります。"}},{"emakis":[{"cat":null,"title":null,"chapter":null,"page_id":null,"scene_id":null,"sort_key":null,"title_en":null,"scroll_id":null},{"cat":null,"src":null,"name":null,"width":null,"config":null,"height":null,"chapter":null,"page_id":null,"sort_key":null,"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_fourth"}],"metadata":{"id":4,"era":"鎌倉","title":"鳥獣人物戯画絵巻 丁巻","author":"鳥羽僧正覚猷","source":{"url":"https://colbase.nich.go.jp/collection_items/tnm/A-1530?locale=ja","name":"鳥獣人戯画絵巻 摸本（ColBase）"},"keyword":[{"id":"caricature","name":"戯画","slug":"caricature"},{"id":"tobae","name":"鳥羽絵","slug":"tobae"},{"id":"buddhism","name":"仏教","slug":"buddhism"}],"scroll_id":"choju-jinbutsu-giga_fourth","personname":[],"description":"鎌倉時代に描かれた「鳥獣人物戯画絵巻」丁巻の摸本です。甲巻、乙巻、丙巻とはまったく異なるタッチで描かれ、タイトル通り「鳥獣戯画」と言いながらも、人間しか登場しません。腕の立つ絵師が、酔った勢いで一気に描き上げたかのような、勢いのある筆致が特徴的です。「番論義に着座した公卿たち」では、座っている4人の公卿のうち、1人だけがリアルな顔（似絵）で描かれているなど、謎めいた部分も多い一巻です。"}}]